    "Cybersecurity firm Check Point Research discovered that hackers had manipulated the configuration of the web testing suite SilverBullet.",
    "This modification allowed them to launch credential stuffing or brute force attacks on ChatGPT accounts, leading to widespread theft of accounts [24].",
